#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: studio317-report-drafts-google-analytics.php includes/class-admin.php:118
#: includes/class-admin.php:119
msgid "Studio317 Report Drafts for Google Analytics"
msgstr "Studio317 Report Drafts for Google Analytics"

#. Description of the plugin
#: studio317-report-drafts-google-analytics.php
msgid ""
"Creates AI-assisted report drafts from GA4 data in the WordPress user "
"language with admin review, editing, and copy tools."
msgstr ""
"GA4データから、WordPressユーザー言語に合わせたAI支援のレポート下書きを作成"
"し、管理画面で確認・編集・コピーできます。"

#. Author of the plugin
#: studio317-report-drafts-google-analytics.php
msgid "Kimiya Watabe / Studio317"
msgstr "Kimiya Watabe / Studio317"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: studio317-report-drafts-google-analytics.php
msgid "https://business.s317.com/"
msgstr "https://business.s317.com/"

#: includes/class-admin.php:129 includes/class-admin.php:130
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:47
msgid "Report Builder"
msgstr "レポートビルダー"

#: includes/class-admin.php:138 includes/class-admin.php:139
#: includes/class-status-page.php:50
msgid "Current Status"
msgstr "現在の状況"

#: includes/class-admin.php:147 includes/class-admin.php:148
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "設定"

#: includes/class-admin.php:198
msgid ""
"Directory scope matches paths that start with the entered path, such as /"
"blog/."
msgstr ""
"ディレクトリ範囲では、/blog/ など入力したパスで始まるページを対象にします。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:199
msgid "Page scope matches the exact normalized path, such as /about."
msgstr "ページ範囲では、/about など正規化された完全一致のパスを対象にします。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:200
msgid "Copied."
msgstr "コピーしました。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:201
msgid "Copy failed. Please select and copy manually."
msgstr "コピーできませんでした。選択して手動でコピーしてください。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:202
msgid "Nothing to copy."
msgstr "コピーする内容がありません。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:266 includes/class-admin.php:359
#: includes/class-admin.php:404
msgid ""
"You do not have permission to manage Studio317 Report Drafts for Google "
"Analytics credentials."
msgstr ""
"Studio317 Report Drafts for Google Analytics の認証情報を管理する権限がありま"
"せん。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:267 includes/class-admin.php:360
#: includes/class-admin.php:405
msgid "Permission denied"
msgstr "権限がありません"

#: includes/class-ai-client.php:142 includes/class-report-builder.php:1054
msgid ""
"AI text generation is unavailable. Configure a compatible text-generation "
"provider in WordPress Settings > Connectors before generating a report draft."
msgstr ""
"AIテキスト生成を利用できません。レポート下書きを生成する前に、WordPress設定 "
"> Connectors で互換性のあるテキスト生成プロバイダーを設定してください。"

#: includes/class-ai-client.php:148
msgid ""
"AI generation did not return usable report text. Review the AI provider "
"configuration and try again."
msgstr ""
"AI生成から利用可能なレポート本文が返されませんでした。AIプロバイダー設定を確"
"認して再試行してください。"

#: includes/class-ai-client.php:155
msgid ""
"AI generation failed. Review the WordPress AI provider configuration and try "
"again. Do not share credentials, request data, provider responses, or "
"generated report content in support requests."
msgstr ""
"AI生成に失敗しました。WordPress のAIプロバイダー設定を確認して再試行してくだ"
"さい。サポート依頼では、認証情報、リクエストデータ、プロバイダーのレスポン"
"ス、生成されたレポート本文を共有しないでください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:258
msgid "GA4 Property ID is not configured."
msgstr "GA4プロパティIDが設定されていません。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:265
msgid ""
"No Google connection is available for GA4 Fetch. Connect Google in Settings "
"and try again."
msgstr ""
"GA4データ取得に使用できるGoogle接続がありません。設定でGoogleに接続してから再"
"試行してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:277
msgid "GA4 report period is invalid."
msgstr "GA4レポート期間が無効です。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:331
msgid ""
"Could not connect to Google Analytics Data API. Check the server network "
"connection and try again."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API に接続できませんでした。サーバーのネットワーク接続"
"を確認して再試行してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:346
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API returned an unreadable response. Please try again "
"later."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API から読み取れないレスポンスが返されました。時間をお"
"いて再試行してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:677 includes/class-ga4-client.php:701
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API rejected the report request. Check the GA4 "
"property ID, date range, and report filters."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API がレポートリクエストを拒否しました。GA4プロパティ"
"ID、期間、レポートフィルターを確認してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:681 includes/class-ga4-client.php:705
msgid ""
"Google credential is invalid or expired. Reconnect Google in Settings and "
"try again."
msgstr ""
"Google認証情報が無効または期限切れです。設定でGoogleに再接続してから再試行し"
"てください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:685 includes/class-ga4-client.php:709
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API permission was denied. Check that the token has "
"access to the selected GA4 property."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API の権限が拒否されました。選択したGA4プロパティにトー"
"クンがアクセスできるか確認してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:689 includes/class-ga4-client.php:713
msgid ""
"GA4 property was not found. Check that the property ID is correct and that "
"the token can access it."
msgstr ""
"GA4プロパティが見つかりません。プロパティIDが正しいことと、トークンがアクセス"
"できることを確認してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:693 includes/class-ga4-client.php:717
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API rate limit may have been exceeded. Please wait and "
"try again later."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API のレート制限に達した可能性があります。しばらく待っ"
"てから再試行してください。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:697 includes/class-ga4-client.php:721
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API is temporarily unavailable. Please try again later."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API は一時的に利用できません。時間をおいて再試行してく"
"ださい。"

#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:724
msgid ""
"Google Analytics Data API returned an unexpected error. Check the settings "
"and try again."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics Data API から予期しないエラーが返されました。設定を確認して"
"再試行してください。"

#. translators: 1: safe user-facing error message, 2: HTTP status code.
#: includes/class-ga4-client.php:759
#, php-format
msgid "%1$s HTTP status: %2$d"
msgstr "%1$s HTTPステータス: %2$d"

#: includes/class-help-dialog.php:28
msgid "Help"
msgstr "ヘルプ"

#: includes/class-help-dialog.php:64
msgid "Close"
msgstr "閉じる"

#: includes/class-help-dialog.php:81
msgid "Server configuration example:"
msgstr "サーバー設定例:"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:50
msgid ""
"AI summarizes data fetched from Google Analytics (GA4) to create a report "
"draft."
msgstr ""
"Google Analytics (GA4) から取得したデータを AI が要約してレポートを作成。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:59
msgid "Report Conditions"
msgstr "レポート条件"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:65 includes/class-report-builder.php:66
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:74
msgid "Data sent to Google Analytics Data API"
msgstr "Google Analytics Data API に送信されるデータ"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:76
msgid ""
"When you click Fetch GA4 Data, the selected date range, comparison setting, "
"data scope, host name/path filters, and required metrics/dimensions are sent "
"to the Google Analytics Data API."
msgstr ""
"「GA4データを取得」をクリックすると、選択した期間、比較設定、データ範囲、ホス"
"ト名・パスのフィルター、必要な指標とディメンションが Google Analytics Data "
"API に送信されます。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:77
msgid "AI provider credentials are not sent to Google by this plugin."
msgstr "このプラグインは AI プロバイダー認証情報を Google に送信しません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:78
msgid ""
"WordPress user identifiers, cookies, and IP addresses are not included in "
"this GA4 request body by design."
msgstr ""
"このGA4リクエスト本文には、設計上、WordPressユーザー識別子、Cookie、IPアドレ"
"スは含まれません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:87 includes/class-report-builder.php:853
msgid "Date Range"
msgstr "期間"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:91
msgid "Start Date"
msgstr "開始日"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:101
msgid "End Date"
msgstr "終了日"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:111
msgid ""
"The default date range is the previous month based on the WordPress timezone."
msgstr "デフォルトの期間は、WordPressのタイムゾーンに基づく前月です。"

#. translators: %d: maximum number of report days.
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:118
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The report period is limited to %d days to keep GA4 requests and report data "
"manageable."
msgstr ""
"GA4リクエストとレポートデータを扱いやすく保つため、レポート期間は%d日までに制"
"限されています。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:128 includes/class-report-builder.php:133
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:861 includes/class-report-builder.php:1409
msgid "Comparison"
msgstr "比較"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:150
msgid ""
"When comparison is enabled, the selected period is shifted to the previous "
"month or previous year and fetched separately from GA4."
msgstr ""
"比較を有効にすると、選択期間を前月または前年にずらした期間をGA4から別途取得し"
"ます。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:157 includes/class-report-builder.php:162
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:877
msgid "Data Scope"
msgstr "データ範囲"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:181
msgid "Path"
msgstr "パス"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:195
msgid ""
"For directory scope, enter a path such as /blog/. For page scope, enter a "
"path such as /about."
msgstr ""
"ディレクトリ範囲では /blog/ のようなパスを入力します。ページ範囲では /about "
"のようなパスを入力します。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:200
msgid ""
"Site scope covers all paths. Directory scope matches paths that start with "
"the entered path. Page scope matches the exact normalized path. Full URLs "
"are not allowed."
msgstr ""
"サイト全体はすべてのパスを対象にします。ディレクトリ範囲は入力したパスで始ま"
"るパスに一致し、ページ範囲は正規化されたパスに完全一致します。完全なURLは使用"
"できません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:209
msgid "Fetch GA4 Data"
msgstr "GA4データを取得"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:214
msgid ""
"Fetch GA4 Data validates the conditions, fetches GA4 preset reports, and "
"creates a Data Preview."
msgstr ""
"「GA4データを取得」では、条件を確認し、GA4のプリセットレポートを取得して送信"
"データのプレビューを作成します。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:241
msgid "You do not have permission to perform this action."
msgstr "この操作を行う権限がありません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:254
msgid "Security check failed. Please reload the page and try again."
msgstr ""
"セキュリティチェックに失敗しました。ページを再読み込みして再試行してくださ"
"い。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:274
msgid "Invalid action."
msgstr "無効な操作です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:511
msgid ""
"The GA4 data could not be converted into valid data for AI generation. "
"Please check the settings and try again."
msgstr ""
"GA4データをAI生成に使用できる有効なデータへ変換できませんでした。設定を確認し"
"て再試行してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:559
msgid ""
"Google connection needs to be renewed before GA4 data can be fetched. Open "
"Settings, reconnect Google, and try again. Credential values are not "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"GA4データを取得する前にGoogle接続の更新が必要です。設定を開いてGoogleに再接続"
"し、再試行してください。認証情報の値は表示されません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:563
msgid ""
"Google connection is not ready for GA4 requests. Open Settings, reconnect "
"Google, and try again. Credential values are not displayed."
msgstr ""
"Google接続はGA4リクエストに使用できる状態ではありません。設定を開いてGoogleに"
"再接続し、再試行してください。認証情報の値は表示されません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:566
msgid ""
"Google connection is not configured. Open Settings, configure Google OAuth, "
"connect your Google account, and try again. Credential values are not "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Google接続が設定されていません。設定を開いてGoogle OAuthを設定し、Googleアカ"
"ウントに接続してから再試行してください。認証情報の値は表示されません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:586
msgid ""
"The saved report data is missing, expired, or no longer valid. Please fetch "
"GA4 data again."
msgstr ""
"一時保存されたレポートデータが見つからない、期限切れ、または無効です。GA4デー"
"タを再取得してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:639
msgid "Start date is invalid."
msgstr "開始日が無効です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:643
msgid "End date is invalid."
msgstr "終了日が無効です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:651
msgid "End date must be the same as or later than start date."
msgstr "終了日は開始日以降の日付にしてください。"

#. translators: %d: maximum report period days.
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:665
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The report period cannot exceed %d days. Please choose a shorter date range."
msgstr ""
"レポート期間は%d日を超えることはできません。より短い期間を選択してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:675
msgid "Comparison option is invalid."
msgstr "比較オプションが無効です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:683
msgid "Data scope is invalid."
msgstr "データ範囲が無効です。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:726
msgid ""
"Comparison period could not be calculated. Please choose a different date "
"range or comparison option."
msgstr ""
"比較期間を計算できませんでした。別の期間または比較オプションを選択してくださ"
"い。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:771
msgid ""
"GA4 data was fetched and the data for AI generation was prepared with "
"warnings."
msgstr "GA4データを取得し、警告付きでAI生成用データを準備しました。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:783
msgid ""
"GA4 preset reports were fetched and the data for AI generation was prepared "
"successfully."
msgstr "GA4のプリセットレポートを取得し、AI生成用データを準備しました。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:793
msgid "AI report was generated."
msgstr "AIレポートを生成しました。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:794
msgid "View the generated report draft."
msgstr "生成レポート下書きを見る。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:817
msgid "Please fix the following errors."
msgstr "以下のエラーを修正してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:848
msgid "Validated Conditions"
msgstr "検証済み条件"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:865 includes/class-report-builder.php:1200
msgid "Comparison Period"
msgstr "比較期間"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:872 includes/class-report-builder.php:886
msgid "None"
msgstr "なし"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:881
msgid "Normalized Path"
msgstr "正規化パス"

#. translators: 1: report language name, 2: output locale.
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:914 includes/class-status-page.php:357
#, php-format
msgid "Report language: %1$s (%2$s)"
msgstr "生成するレポートの言語: %1$s（%2$s）"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:944
msgid "AI Data Preview"
msgstr "AI送信データのプレビュー"

#. translators: %d: number of minutes the report data is saved temporarily.
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:950
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The data to be sent through the WordPress AI Client has been saved "
"temporarily for %d minutes."
msgstr "WordPress AI Client を通じて送信するデータを%d分間一時保存しました。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:957
msgid ""
"The reviewed report data is stored temporarily for this user and expires "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"確認済みのレポートデータはこのユーザー向けに一時保存され、自動的に期限切れに"
"なります。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:973
msgid "Structured pre-send review"
msgstr "送信前の構造化レビュー"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:976
msgid "Review this structured summary before sending data to AI."
msgstr "AIにデータを送信する前に、この構造化された要約を確認してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:980
msgid ""
"This preview focuses on report conditions, data availability, warnings, and "
"generation readiness."
msgstr ""
"このプレビューでは、レポート条件、データの利用可否、警告、生成準備状況を確認"
"できます。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:984
msgid ""
"Use the status and warning information below to decide whether to generate a "
"report."
msgstr "以下の状態と警告情報を確認して、レポートを生成するか判断してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:988
msgid ""
"The reviewed report data can include host name, page path, traffic channel/"
"source, city/country regional labels, summary metrics, and comparison "
"differences."
msgstr ""
"確認済みのレポートデータには、ホスト名、ページパス、トラフィックチャネル/ソー"
"ス、都市/国の地域ラベル、概要指標、比較差分が含まれる場合があります。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:992
msgid ""
"Credentials are not included in the data sent through the WordPress AI "
"Client. Google access tokens, AI provider credentials, GA4 Property ID, "
"WordPress user identifiers, cookies, and IP addresses are not included by "
"design."
msgstr ""
"WordPress AI Client を通じて送信するデータに認証情報は含まれません。Googleア"
"クセストークン、AIプロバイダー認証情報、GA4プロパティID、WordPressユーザー識"
"別子、Cookie、IPアドレスは設計上含まれません。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:996
msgid ""
"Page paths and traffic sources can still be sensitive business analytics "
"information, so review the data before sending it."
msgstr ""
"ページパスやトラフィックソースは機密性のあるビジネス分析情報になり得るため、"
"送信前にデータを確認してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1000
msgid ""
"For support, share visible status messages, warning messages, or general "
"error names only. Do not share credentials, option values, request or "
"response bodies, AI data JSON, generated report text, screenshots, or "
"browser Network evidence."
msgstr ""
"サポートには、表示されている状態メッセージ、警告メッセージ、または一般的なエ"
"ラー名のみを共有してください。認証情報、オプション値、リクエスト/レスポンス本"
"文、AI送信データのJSON、生成レポート本文、スクリーンショット、ブラウザの"
"Network証跡は共有しないでください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1005
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1194
msgid "Daily Trend"
msgstr "日別推移"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1006
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1195
msgid "Top Pages"
msgstr "上位ページ"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1007
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1196
msgid "Traffic Channels"
msgstr "トラフィックチャネル"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1008
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1197
msgid "Traffic Sources"
msgstr "トラフィックソース"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1009
#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1198
msgid "Regional Trends"
msgstr "地域別推移"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1012
msgid "Data sent through the WordPress AI Client"
msgstr "WordPress AI Client を通じて送信されるデータ"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1015
msgid ""
"When you generate an AI report, the reviewed report data and selected report "
"language are sent through the WordPress AI Client to the AI provider "
"configured by the site administrator."
msgstr ""
"AIレポートを生成すると、確認済みのレポートデータと選択されたレポート言語が、"
"WordPress AI Client を通じてサイト管理者が設定したAIプロバイダーへ送信されま"
"す。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1019
msgid ""
"Generating a report may consume usage with the configured AI provider. "
"Provider terms, privacy practices, billing, retention, and credential "
"management depend on the provider configured through WordPress."
msgstr ""
"レポート生成では、設定済みのAIプロバイダーの利用量を消費する場合があります。"
"プロバイダーの規約、プライバシー慣行、課金、保持、認証情報管理は、WordPress "
"で設定されたプロバイダーに依存します。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1023
msgid ""
"The generated result is a draft. Review and edit it before publishing, "
"sharing, or sending it."
msgstr "生成結果は下書きです。公開、共有、送信の前に確認・編集してください。"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1037
msgid "The current report text will be overwritten. Continue?"
msgstr "現在のレポート本文が上書きされます。続行しますか？"

#: includes/class-report-builder.php:1042
msgid "Regenerate AI Report"
msgstr "AIレポートを再生成"

